      "medical_standards": "KDOQI (and other international renal guidelines) recommend a minimum of thrice-weekly dialysis (Kt/V ≥ 1.2 per session or equivalent weekly dialysis dose) for most patients on maintenance haemodialysis. There is no standard clinical justification to reduce HDF frequency compared with HD.",
